Package com.github.thorbenkuck.netcom2.network.shared.comm.model Description

This package contains all Data-Objects, used within NetCom2.

All of those Data-Objects are final and immutable. It is not possible and not intended to change or extend those.

Note that all of those are annotated with APILevel, so that they might be subject to change. This is not very likely, but do not rely on those.
